.\" Manpage for yayfzf
.TH yayfzf 1 "2026-01-06" "2.0.2" "yayfzf manual"

.SH NAME
yayfzf \- interactively search, install, and remove AUR packages using fzf


.SH SYNOPSIS
.B yayfzf [\fIOPTIONS\fR] [\fISEARCH QUERY\fR]


.SH DESCRIPTION
Search, install, and remove packages from the AUR interactively with fzf.


.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-h
Show the help menu

.TP
.B \-\-help
Show the extended help menu

.TP
.B \-k, \-\-keybindings
List keybindings for yayfzf

.TP
.B \-V, \-\-version
Show version of yayfzf

.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
.B $ yayfzf
Run yayfzf with no search query

.TP
.B $ yayfzf fzf
Search for 'fzf' with yayfzf

.TP
.B $ yayfzf \-h
Show the help menu


